"title": "1145: God, transcendence of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "1145",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>God is far above, beyond and outside the created order.</p>\n<h2>God is outside and above all creation</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps113:4\">PSA 113:4</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:22\">ISA 40:22</a></strong> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:27\">1KI 8:27</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr2:6\">2CH 2:6</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job37:23\">JOB 37:23</a> <em>Elihu declares the LORD to be beyond reach</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps8:1\">PSA 8:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps57:5\">PSA 57:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps57:11\">PSA 57:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps97:9\">PSA 97:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps108:5\">PSA 108:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps148:13\">PSA 148:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa33:5\">ISA 33:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:49\">ACT 7:49</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:24\">ACT 17:24</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:20-Eph1:21\">EPH 1:20–1:21</a> <em>Jesus Christ is above all, in the place of highest honour and authority</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:6\">EPH 4:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb7:26\">HEB 7:26</a></p>\n<h2>God is able also to draw near to his creatures</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa57:15\">ISA 57:15</a></strong></p>\n<h2>The invisibility of God</h2>\n<h3>God is invisible to people and hidden from their sight</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod33:20\">EXO 33:20</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa45:15\">ISA 45:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod3:6\">EXO 3:6</a>JOB <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod9:11\">9:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job23:8-Job23:9\">JOB 23:8–23:9</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps10:1\">PSA 10:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps13:1\">PSA 13:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:46\">PSA 89:46</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:18\">JHN 1:18</a> <em>Jesus Christ has made God known</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:37\">JHN 5:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:15\">COL 1:15</a> <em>Jesus Christ is the image of God</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:17\">1TI 1:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:16\">1TI 6:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:12\">1JN 4:12</a></p>\n<h3>OT saints who saw God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod33:11\">EXO 33:11</a></strong> <em>These exceptions indicate that God's invisibility is not inherent, but the result of sinful people's inability to look upon a holy God.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen32:30\">GEN 32:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod24:10\">EXO 24:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg13:22\">JDG 13:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa6:5\">ISA 6:5</a></p>\n<h3>God is made visible in Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:18\">JHN 1:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:9\">JHN 14:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:4\">2CO 4:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:6\">2CO 4:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:15\">COL 1:15</a></p>\n<h3>Redeemed people will be able to look at God's face</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:8\">MAT 5:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor13:12\">1CO 13:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:2\">1JN 3:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:4\">REV 22:4</a></p>\n<h2>God's ways are beyond human understanding</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:8-Isa55:9\">ISA 55:8–55:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut29:29\">DEU 29:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job5:9\">JOB 5:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job11:7\">JOB 11:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job36:22-Job36:23\">JOB 36:22–36:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps139:1-Ps139:6\">PSA 139:1–139:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov25:2\">PRO 25:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl3:11\">ECC 3:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:28\">ISA 40:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:33-Rom11:34\">ROM 11:33–11:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:11\">1CO 2:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:16\">1CO 2:16</a></p>",
